            <p class="mb-4">
               <strong class="text-gray-900 text-2xl block mb-4 italic">Ryoji Hido (氷堂リョージ)</strong>
               Ryoji Hido is a Japanese manga artist who publishes under two pen names: Ryoji Hido (氷堂涼二) and Ryoji Hido (氷堂リョージ). The latter name, which he had been using since his middle school days and throughout his doujinshi period, was officially adopted when he debuted in the 4-panel manga magazine Manga Club. He chose this name to appeal to a broader audience, and has since used it for all subsequent publications.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4">
